@startuml workflow_state
title HealthAI - Case Status Lifecycle (app/cases/transitions.py)

[*] --> NEW : create_case

NEW --> EXTRACTED : assemble_case / attach_extraction
NEW --> REJECTED

EXTRACTED --> REVIEWED : attach_review
EXTRACTED --> REJECTED

REVIEWED --> APPEAL_GENERATED : attach_appeal
REVIEWED --> REJECTED

APPEAL_GENERATED --> PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW : (auto on attach_appeal)
APPEAL_GENERATED --> REJECTED

PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW --> APPROVED_FOR_EXPORT : human APPROVE
PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW --> REJECTED : human REJECT
PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW --> APPEAL_GENERATED : human REQUEST_CHANGES

APPROVED_FOR_EXPORT --> REJECTED
REJECTED --> APPEAL_GENERATED : reopen

APPROVED_FOR_EXPORT --> [*] : export bundle

note right of PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW
  REQUEST_CHANGES re-queues:
  APPEAL_GENERATED -> PENDING_HUMAN_REVIEW
end note

note bottom
  Every transition records a STATUS_CHANGED AuditEvent.
  Illegal transitions raise InvalidTransitionError.
end note

@enduml
